  "detailed_description": "Hello Teacher is a VHS PSX multiplayer horror game where a group of children try to run and hide from evil teacher. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1387970/extras/67f85a82c5e71e47e040571abfc7cd90.poster.avif?t=1671997021\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1387970/extras/67f85a82c5e71e47e040571abfc7cd90.webm?t=1671997021\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1387970/extras/67f85a82c5e71e47e040571abfc7cd90.mp4?t=1671997021\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>When you join game its randomly choose a teacher. He need to catch all kids. Children need to escape from school and hide from teacher. Use your skills to win.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1387970/extras/5dfc4d7bd4664f0435bbbfc911186eba.poster.avif?t=1671997021\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1387970/extras/5dfc4d7bd4664f0435bbbfc911186eba.webm?t=1671997021\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1387970/extras/5dfc4d7bd4664f0435bbbfc911186eba.mp4?t=1671997021\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
